]

Rules:
- source_ids: 1–3 IDs from the source list above
- objective_ids: 1–3 IDs from the objectives list above — which objectives this episode advances
- podcast_topic: actionable and specific — this directly drives podcast audio generation
- key_concepts: 2–5 precise terms or ideas
- ai_summary: exactly 3 sentences, concrete and specific (not generic)
- Return ONLY the JSON array, nothing else
